{"tid":2431757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防範中共影響 猶他州眾院通過決議要求關閉該州孔子學院","createTime":"2021-03-04T01:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T04:32:50.000Z","uid":138409,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36ddef675f4711a507f3724763357ec6daf5560c","tid":2431757,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:10:36.000Z","msg":"決議全文：<a href=\"https://le.utah.gov/~2021/bills/static/HR0008.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fle.utah.gov%2F~2021%2Fbills%2Fstatic%2FHR0008.html&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX1Scv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=44c222ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://le.utah.gov/~2021/bills/static/HR0008.html</a><br />\n（要用VPN駁去美國先睇到）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/utah-house-to-close-confucius-schools-20210303/5801005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Futah-house-to-close-confucius-schools-20210303%2F5801005.html&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX1Scv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=614fc654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/utah-house-to-close-confucius-schools-20210303/5801005.html</a><br />\n美國猶他州眾議院通過決議案，要求關閉該州由中國政府資助的孔子學院。<br />\n<br />\n《鹽湖城論壇報》（Salt Lake Tribune）3月2日報導，州眾議院當天通過一項決議案，要求該州的兩所大學關閉校內尚未關閉的孔子學院，理由是孔子學院可能幫助中國共產黨的間諜活動，對美國國家安全構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n猶他州的州眾議院之前曾通過了一項參眾兩院聯合決議案，但在州參議院沒有付諸表決的情況下，州眾議院星期二夜晚再度表決，以69票比1票，單獨以州眾議院名義通過了《保護猶他高等教育機構免受中國共產黨影響的決議》。<br />\n<br />\n目前尚不清楚州參議院為何沒有就這項決議案舉行聽證。參議院主席之前對這項決議案表示過擔憂，表示將審視議案內容是否會影響到猶他州與中國的貿易關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n州眾議院通過的決議案建議猶他州繼續經營孔子學院的猶他大學（University of Utah）和南猶他大學（Southern Utah University）在2022年12月1日前關閉孔院。<br />\n<br />\n猶他大學發言人在給《鹽湖城論壇報》的一份聲明中說，<span class=\"gold\">學校已經計劃在2023年中期關閉孔院，由於這項決議案的通過，已經決定提前大約六個月關閉孔院。</span><br />\n<br />\n南猶他大學發言人之前表示，如果決議案獲得通過，該校將落實決議案的要求，&ldquo;開始準備關閉孔子學院。&rdquo;可目前決議案只是在州眾議院過關，尚不清楚南猶他大學是否還會這樣做。"},{"pid":"8d14972b3c308b4f47cc1013ae1f69f4306795bc","tid":2431757,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:14:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28630d97f15e19ee4b5dbf5b718d20aeafbf4925","tid":2431757,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:15:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c6ce1a46549aaa3e5661a35c423e3e99e2d57054","tid":2431757,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"中共之後可以整個一帶一路非洲黑人孔子學院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8078fd5da74151dfa08a66dd4ace1710e9747497","tid":2431757,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"恐怕就嚟排華"},{"pid":"8164334d1ea2287405437dae266a8f24ef891b33","tid":2431757,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:21:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"42a800e9f02f4d99cb3a2ddc48e29613f3b49926","tid":2431757,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:24:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"09fbe06262525e4e40bb32b480dc0419af78b2cf","tid":2431757,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99f47cbe4f31e760586069dd9ca424d82128f5db","tid":2431757,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:28:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bbafaa018b16802305df70df49d0785cbad9b9cd","tid":2431757,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8078fd5da74151dfa08a66dd4ace1710e9747497","tid":2431757,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"恐怕就嚟排華"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"整個 ALM<br />\nAsians lives matter."},{"pid":"775cfcf5b144867bf657f96439ae46a00f3cc3ad","tid":2431757,"uid":272371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbafaa018b16802305df70df49d0785cbad9b9cd","tid":2431757,"uid":301523,"like